Interface ELFSymbol


  • public interface ELFSymbol

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int BINDING_GLOBAL
      Binding specifying that global symbols are visible to all object files being combined.
      static int BINDING_HIPROC
      Upper bound binding values reserverd for processor specific semantics.
      static int BINDING_LOCAL
      Binding specifying that local symbols are not visible outside the object file that contains its definition.
      static int BINDING_LOPROC
      Lower bound binding values reserverd for processor specific semantics.
      static int BINDING_WEAK
      Binding secifying that the symbol resembles a global symbol, but has a lower precedence.
      static byte TYPE_FILE
      Type defining that the symbol is associated with a file.
      static byte TYPE_FUNCTION
      Type specifying that the symbol is associated with a function.
      static byte TYPE_HIPROC
      Upper bound type reserved for processor specific semantics.
      static byte TYPE_LOPROC
      Lower bound type reserved for processor specific semantics.
      static byte TYPE_NOOBJECT
      Type specifying that the symbol is unspecified.
      static byte TYPE_OBJECT
      Type specifying that the symbol is associated with an object.
      static byte TYPE_SECTION
      Type specifying that the symbol is associated with a section.
